1:# System Architecture
11:## 1. Architectural Style: Modular Monolith
15:### 1.1 Layered Structure (Per Module)
17:- **Application Layer**: Server Actions and Services in `lib/{module}/application/`.
18:- **Domain Layer**: Entities and business logic in `lib/{module}/domain/`.
23:## 2. Component Design
25:### 2.1 Component Overview
29:| **App Shell** | PWA Layout, Navigation, Auth Guards | Next.js, shadcn/ui |
30:| **Auth** | Registration, Login, Session Mgmt | Auth.js v5 |
31:| **Tracker** | Dose Logging, Protocols, PWA Sync | React, TanStack Query |
34:| **Ordering** | Vendor Catalog, Telegram MTProto | GramJS, Server Actions |
36:| **Audit** | Immutable Mutation Logs | Prisma (Postgres) |
41:## 3. Data Flows
43:### 3.1 Flow: Log a Dose (Offline-First)
49:   - **Case: Logged**: Validate `idempotencyKey`, decrement `Vial.remainingMg` (if vial linked), write `DoseLog`, write `AuditLog`.
50:   - **Case: Skipped**: Write `DoseLog` (status: Skipped), write `AuditLog`.
51:   - **Case: Edited**: Only allowed same calendar day; update `DoseLog`, adjust `Vial`, write `AuditLog`.
53:### 3.2 Flow: Place Telegram Order (Payment Safety Gate)
58:5. **Audit**: Every status transition emits a signed `AuditEvent`.
62:## 4. Module Structure (Bounded Context Slices)
72:│   ├── ordering/               # Isolated Ordering UI (ADR-015)
73:│   ├── actions/                # Server Action Entrypoints (grouped by context)
79:│       └── sync/               # PWA Sync Handler
80:├── lib/                        # Core Logic (Domain & Application)
84:│   │   └── infrastructure/     # Prisma repos, external API clients
85:│   ├── jobs/                   # Background job implementations
93:## 5. State Management Design
95:- **Server State (TanStack Query)**: MTProto connection, Sync status, Adherence metrics.
96:- **Client UI State (React Context)**: Onboarding wizard, Ordering cart.
97:- **Client Persistence (IndexedDB)**: Offline dose log queue, optimistic inventory projection.
101:## 6. Scheduled Jobs (Railway Cron)
107:| **Audit Purge** | Daily | Delete `AuditEvent` records > 90 days old. |
112:## 7. Deployment Topology
114:- **Runtime**: Node.js 20 on Railway Container (Always-on for MTProto).
122:## 8. Failure Modes
124:- **MTProto Logout**: Session invalidated; system falls back to display message + deep-link.
125:- **Offline Sync Conflict**: Idempotency key `user:protocol:date` wins.
126:- **Audit Write Failure**: Mutation rolled back via DB transaction.
130:## 9. Testing Architecture
134:- **Integration Tests (Vitest)**: Server Actions, repository transactions, MTProto session encryption.
137:  - **Critical Path**: Offline dose log queuing and sync replay.
138:  - **Auth**: Managed user invitation and permission isolation.

